Chapter 1 is COMPLETE so do NOT include it.

For chapters 2 through 15, create the following tasks per chapter. Use the chapter info below for naming.

Per chapter task pattern (using chapter 2 as example):
1. Chapter preface: id='ch02-preface', title='Write Chapter 2 Preface: LLM / Generative AI', target_persona='TechWriter', tags=['preface','chapter02']
2. For each recipe 1-10: 
