   b. Draft python companion: id='ch02-r01-python', title='Draft Ch2 Recipe 1 Python Companion', target_persona='TechWriter', depends_on=['ch02-r01-draft'], tags=['python','chapter02']
   c. Code review: id='ch02-r01-code-review', title='Code Review Ch2 Recipe 1', target_persona='TechCodeReviewer', depends_on=['ch02-r01-python'], tags=['review','chapter02','code-review']
   d. Expert review: id='ch02-r01-expert-review', title='Expert Review Ch2 Recipe 1', target_persona='TechExpertReviewer', depends_on=['ch02-r01-draft'], tags=['review','chapter02','expert-review']
   e. Final edit: id='ch02-r01-edit', title='Edit Ch2 Recipe 1', target_persona='TechEditor', depends_on=['ch02-r01-code-review','ch02-r01-expert-review'], tags=['edit','chapter02']
3. Chapter index: id='ch02-index', title='Write Chapter 2 Index', target_persona='TechWriter', depends_on (all 10 edit tasks for that chapter), tags=['index','chapter02']

Priority scheme: chapter number * 100 + task order within chapter. So ch02 tasks start at priority 200, ch03 at 300, etc. Within a chapter: preface=1, recipe drafts=10-19, python=20-29, code-review=30-39, expert-review=40-49, edit=50-59, index=90.

