- Ch2: LLM / Generative AI (recipes: 'Clinical Note Summarization', 'Patient-Friendly Discharge Instructions', 'Prior Authorization Letter Generation', 'Medical Literature Q&A', 'Radiology Report Generation', 'Clinical Trial Matching', 'Medication Interaction Explanation', 'Synthetic Patient Data Generation', 'Multi-lingual Patient Communication', 'Clinical Decision Support Augmentation')
